I am no fan of complex legal texts -- so here's the TL;DR
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  [OK]   You CAN:
         - use it for ANY purpose: personal, commercial, academic, government,
           military -- no field-of-use limits
         - modify it, redistribute it, sell it
         - build closed-source / proprietary products on top of it

  [KEEP] You MUST:
         - keep the copyright notice and this License in the code
         - ship a visible, up-to-date Contributors list (Contributors.md) with
           every release -- in the source or as an appendix

  [NAME] Don't use the names of the Licensor or the Contributors, or the name of
         this License, to endorse or promote your product without written
         permission.

This TL;DR is for orientation only and is NOT the license. If anything here
conflicts with the FULL LICENSE TEXT below, the FULL LICENSE TEXT governs.


